n class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/gamingvillager">GamingVillager</a></span><span title="2025-09-02 01:56:18" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/14005680">198 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hey I used your sprites for my recent game project. It&#x27;s my most popular game yet so I really appreciate your hard work helping me along with it.<br><a href="https://gx.games/games/64tuf3/no-hit-run/" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://gx.games/games/64tuf3/no-hit-run/</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:13639525,&quot;user_id&quot;:8574786}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-13639525"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/hukto-he" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/hukto-he">HukTo_He</a></span><span title="2025-08-04 20:11:49" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13639525">226 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Liked that Dino. I made few animations to him, idle and forward/backward walk</p><p><a href="https://hukto-he.itch.io/0x72-dungeon-tileset-2-dino-character">https://hukto-he.itch.io/0x72-dungeon-tileset-2-dino-character<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1hZ2UvMzc4ODMzNy8yMjU3NTgxNi5wbmc=/original/A56T5S.png" loading="lazy"></a><br></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:14707067,&quot;user_id&quot;:54608}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column" id="post-14707067"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/0x72" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE5NzEwNTEucG5n/25x2