/alpha-vampirrrrtest-name">https://topcrasava.itch.io/alpha-vampirrrrtest-name</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:13242454,&quot;user_id&quot;:13785567}" class="community_post disabled is_deleted has_vote_column" id="post-13242454"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><div class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://static.itch.io/images/frog-sad.svg)" class="post_avatar"></div></div><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><strong class="name_placeholder">Deleted account</strong></span><span title="2025-06-29 20:07:23" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13242454">262 days ago</a></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body"><em class="deleted_message">Deleted post</em></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:13073210,&quot;user_id&quot;:13796307}" class="community_post has_replies has_vote_column" id="post-13073210"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/arcanepurgatory" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIxNTUxMDExLnBuZw==/25x25%23/SWjzLa.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/arcanepurgatory">ArcanePurgatory</a></span><span title="2025-06-06 05:37:08" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13073210">285 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span><span class="downvotes">(-1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hey, im making a game using these sprites, thpught you might want to check it out!! Havent built the credits yet, but as soon as i do ill make sure to add a link to your page!!! Thanks for your awesome work!!</p><p><a href="https://arcanepurgatory.itch.io/arcane-purgatory">https://arcanepurgatory.itch.io/arcane-purgatory</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:13103159,&quot;user_id&quot;:54608}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column" id="post-13103159"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/0x72" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE5NzEwNTEucG5n/25x25%23/rllnE7.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/0x72">0x72</a></span><span title="2025-06-10 08:24:53" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/13103159">281 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>&lt;3</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:12920210,&quot;user_id&quot;:2372491}" class="community_post has_vote_column" id="post-12920210"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href=