amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" data-register_action="community_vote" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" role="img" width="20" aria-hidden height="20" version="1.1" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axeweilder43" class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/axeweilder43">axeweilder43</a></span><span title="2025-05-21 04:13:27" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/12912606">301 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+2)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>mashed v1 + v2 and more this has taken awhile and i&#x27;m here to give show you 1years work combining your two versions together + more&nbsp;<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIxMjg3OTYwLnBuZw==/original/ZgGfdi.png" loading="lazy"></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=https%3A%2F%2F0x72.itch.io%2Fdungeontileset-ii" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;id&quot;:12913943,&quot;user_id&quot;:54608}" class="community_post is_reply has_vote_column" id="post-12913943"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a href="https://itch.io/login?intent=community&amp;return_to=h